Privacy Policy

Effective Date: [7/30/2024]

1. Introduction

Quran Ayats ("we", "our", "us") operates the Quran Ayats application ("App"). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our App. Please read this policy carefully to understand how we handle your personal data.

2. Information We Collect

2.1 Personal Data

As an open-source app, Quran Ayats does not require you to sign up or log in. We do not collect personal data such as your name, email address, or any other personal information.

2.2 Usage Data

We may automatically collect certain information when you use the App. This information does not reveal your specific identity but may include device information, usage data, and other technical data related to how you interact with the App. This data helps us improve the functionality and user experience of the App.

3. How We Use Your Information

Since we do not collect personal data, our primary focus is on improving the App's performance and functionality based on anonymous usage data. The information we collect may be used for:

    Improving the user experience and App functionality
    Providing regular or specific day alerts for selected Ayats and topics
    Offering relevant content based on your topic selection

4. Disclosure of Your Information

As we do not collect personal data, there are limited circumstances under which we would share any information. However, in the interest of transparency:

    We may share anonymous usage data with service providers who assist us in improving the App's performance.
    We may disclose information as required by law or to protect our rights.

5. Data Security

We take the security of your data seriously and implement appropriate measures to protect any information collected through the App. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure.

6. Data Retention

Since we do not collect personal data, there is no retention of such information. Usage data may be retained for analysis purposes to improve the App's functionality.

7. Your Data Protection Rights

As there is no personal data collection, the typical data protection rights may not apply. However, should you have concerns or questions, feel free to contact us.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we encourage you to review this policy periodically.

9. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: support@ayatalert.com
